 <name>AntiMicro</name>
 <summary>Graphical program used to map keyboard buttons and mouse controls to a gamepad</summary>
 <description>
   <p>
     AntiMicro is a graphical program used to map keyboard keys and mouse 
     controls to a gamepad. This program is useful for playing PC games using a
     gamepad that do not have any form of built-in gamepad support. 
   </p>
   <p>
     AntiMicro was inspired by QJoyPad but has additional features.
   </p>
 </description>
